This product bundles lookup data derived from the following public-sector
sources. The code in this product is MIT-licensed (see LICENSE); the bundled
datasets carry the attribution requirements of their respective sources.

----

IFSC (Indian Financial System Code) bank/branch directory
  Source: Reserve Bank of India — "List of NEFT/RTGS enabled bank branches"
  URL:    https://www.rbi.org.in
  Notes:  Republished here for offline lookup. Refreshed monthly via the
          data-refresh workflow; users requiring authoritative real-time
          data should consult the RBI source directly.

Pincode directory
  Source: Department of Posts, Government of India — "All India Pincode
          Directory"
  URL:    https://www.indiapost.gov.in
  Notes:  Public-domain dataset. India Post is the authoritative source;
          this redistribution is for offline lookup convenience.

HSN code -> GST rate mappings
  Source: Central Board of Indirect Taxes and Customs (CBIC) — GST rate
          notifications under the CGST/IGST Acts
  URL:    https://www.cbic.gov.in
  Notes:  Rate changes are issued by CBIC notification; bundled rates
          reflect the most recent refresh and may lag the latest
          notification. Users should consult CBIC for binding rates.

RTO (Regional Transport Office) directory
  Source: State transport-department public listings (compiled per state).
  Notes:  No single authoritative source exists; entries are compiled from
          publicly available state RTO directories.

GST state codes
  Source: Goods and Services Tax Network (GSTN) — public state-code list,
          aligned with the First Schedule of the GST Act.
  Notes:  Includes legacy codes (25 Daman and Diu pre-2020-merger; 28
          Andhra Pradesh pre-bifurcation) so legacy GSTINs remain resolvable.

